PowerSlim - An implementation of FitNesse Slim in PowerShell

Example:

!define TEST_SYSTEM (slim)
!define COMMAND_PATTERN (PowerShell C:\slim.ps1)

!|Query:Script|get-service *Time|
|DisplayName|Status|
|Windows Time|Running|

|script|Script|
|check|eval|6+9|15|
|eval|$global:y=10|
|eval|$global:x = 6|
|check|eval|$x|6|
|check|eval|$y|10|
|check|eval|$x+$y|16|
|check|eval|$x*$y|60|
|check|eval|"Hello World!"|Hello World!|
